  "title" : "Is there a way to automatically generate getters and setters in Eclipse?",
  "body" : "<p>I am working on a new <code>Android</code> project (<code>Java</code>), and created an Object with a large number of variables. Since I am planning to add getters and setters for all of them, I was wondering: is there a shortcut in <code>Eclipse</code> for automatically generating the getters and setters in a given class?</p>\n"
